reviewtext: I thought I was buying the Kensington 64068 but what I received from Amazon was a discontinued 64084 commercial model with an "HP approved" logo on the box and black HP-branded keys.  It works Ok but looks cheaper than the model in the illustration.  It's not worth the trouble of returning but I feel somewhat cheated since I saw an identical unit on eBay [...].
summary: Amazon switched out for a cheaper model!
